{"tid":2194017,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[救快必 記者入]  03年港府倡議：煽動暴力示威並不構成「煽動叛亂罪」！","createTime":"2020-09-08T09:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T16:18:25.000Z","uid":219007,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"371f6370c99f304b7a9b8e7d19f4151f3823d4eb","tid":2194017,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:09:02.000Z","msg":"今日政府又搬龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好快會delete 2003年pdf<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n03年政府諮詢23條時候指現時《刑事罪行條例》9及10條 （告快必個幾條）係涵義太闊，建議大幅度收窄。<br />\n<br />\nBackup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/info/basiclaw23_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fbasiclaw23_c.pdf&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=64e27868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/info/basiclaw23_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAatQ1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAatQ1Y.png&h=8493f15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦以普通法原則下解釋何謂「煽動」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/btsoEVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbtsoEVk.png&h=5b7f985f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府舉例指：參與遊行示威時，煽動他人作出刑事行為，如暴力或燒毁汽車。 <span class=\"red\"><strong>該行為不是屬於煽動叛亂</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hz5Q4m3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhz5Q4m3.png&h=e5c064a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以政府鳩噏話23條立法等建議內容完全符合國際人權公約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kcbs6Ar.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcbs6Ar.png&h=744373f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃毓民解釋廿三條法律背景同當年諮詢過程<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C53CfWflEu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC53CfWflEu8&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=d82e2418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C53CfWflEu8</a> <br />\n二十三條立法諮詢文件對「煽動」定義講得好清楚 黃毓民 毓民踩場<br />\n<br />\n如今李桂華又鳩up了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;<strong><em>警方國家安全處高級警司李桂華表示，被捕人為一名47歲男子，他在6月底至8月間在九龍區舉行29次街站，「巧立名目係防疫講座，實際內容係引起人蔑視政府、引起民間不滿」。他指對方並非以《港區國安法》被捕，但承認調查初段曾以違反《國安法》第21條為方向，惟調查後認為「最適合都係用呢個煽動文字處理」。</em></strong>&rsquo;<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">記者朋友，你哋去咗邊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c286e910261551dc01b61be9da88d8df3db760","tid":2194017,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8838d5d171bb32ef295b56e022d23063a8472773","tid":2194017,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"港共：咁串？咁告你煽動顛覆國家政權罪囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74812f6b60f5c997093e080b149d48c6b4ab4b3","tid":2194017,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68c286e910261551dc01b61be9da88d8df3db760","tid":2194017,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"其實一直都冇人理你條傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860f4e0058f6052a891636163320c77ac1a2a0c1","tid":2194017,"uid":336400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime